       <div class="row-fluid title-container">
        <div class="container">
         <h2 class="clear">
          The Curious Art of the Book Cover
         </h2>
         <div class="blurb">
          <p>
           <em>
            Kleine Welt
           </em>
           , on view through April 5, presents a collection of book covers and new work by Zachary Cahill, R. H. Quaytman, and David Schutter.
          </p>
          <p>
           <a href="https://neubauercollegium.uchicago.edu/exhibitions/current_exhibition/">
            Read more about this topic »
           </a>
          </p>
