         <h2 class="clear">
          Restless Inquiries
         </h2>
         <div class="blurb">
          <p>
           A new report explores the impact of the first five years of humanistic research collaborations at the Neubauer Collegium and charts a path for the years to come.
          </p>
          <p>
           <a href="https://neubauercollegium.uchicago.edu/news/detail/restless_inquiries/">
